                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290910-278-off1533 t18290910-278-crimeloc1535"></join> - I told him to walk on; he got a little way before me: I saw the prisoner take the cap off his head, and give it to a lesser one, who ran away - I collared the prisoner, but the other with the cap got away.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290910-278-person2612">
                  JAMES 
                  ROBERTS
               <interp inst="t18290910-278-person2612" type="surname" value="ROBERTS"></interp>
