                     <interp inst="t18290910-278-person2612" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer, and took the prisoner - he said he knew nothing of it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. The woman cried out Stop him! I stopped - she came up, and said had I the child's cap; I said, "What cap? search me - I have no cap;" she laid hold of me - she said she was not sure of the man, but she would be paid for her cap.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290910-278-person2613">
                  SOPHIA 
                  READING
